  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db3\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A meeting of party leaders will be called again tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs is scheduled to be held tomorrow (11) at 2.00 pm under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena to discuss the future political affairs of the country.",
        "After Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa leaves the presidency, the appointment of a new president and the formation of a new government will be discussed here.",
        "Meanwhile, it is reported that the main political parties have held several special discussions today regarding the current situation in the country."
      ],
